nhc_headline: ...HUMBERTO RAPIDLY STRENGTHENS TO A MAJOR HURRICANE... ...FURTHER INTENSIFICATION EXPECTED OVER THE CENTRAL ATLANTIC...
summary: ...HUMBERTO RAPIDLY STRENGTHENS TO A MAJOR HURRICANE... ...FURTHER INTENSIFICATION EXPECTED OVER THE CENTRAL ATLANTIC... As of 5:00 PM AST Fri Sep 26 the center of Humberto was located near 22.3, -58.1 with movement WNW at 5 mph. The minimum central pressure was 962 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 115 mph.
